e, you can look at a face-down spell or permanent you control. You can’t look at face-down spells or permanents you don’t control unless an effect instructs you to do so.£9/20/2014: You must ensure that your face-down spells and permanents can easily be differentiated from each other. You’re not allowed to mix up the cards that represent them on the battlefield in order to confuse other players. The order they entered the battlefield should remain clear. Common methods for doing this include using markers or dice, or simply placing them in order on the battlefield.£9/20/2014: If a face-down permanent leaves the battlefield, you must reveal it. You must also reveal all face-down spells and permanents you control if you leave the game or if the game ends.','R',NULL,'0.1','0.49','1.49',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R','侦猎犬人','偵獵犬人','Traqueur aïnok','Ainok-Spurensucher','Ainok Battipista','アイノクの足跡追い','Rastreador Ainok','Аинок-Следопыт','Rastreador ainok','아이녹 추적꾼','生物～猎犬／斥候','生物～獵犬／斥候','Créature : chien de chasse et éclaireur','Kreatur — Hund, Späher','Creatura — Esploratore Segugio','クリーチャー ― 猟犬・スカウト','Criatura — Sabujo Batedor','Существо — Пес Разведчик','Criatura — Explorador perro','생물 — 사냥개 정찰병','先攻£变身{4}{R}（你可牌面朝下地施放此牌并支付{3}，将其当成2/2生物。可随时支付其变身费用使其翻回正面。）','先攻£變身{4}{R}（你可牌面朝下地施放此牌並支付{3}，將其當成2/2生物。可隨時支付其變身費用使其翻回正面。）','Initiative£Mue {4}{R} #_(Vous pouvez lancer cette carte face cachée comme une créature 2/2 pour {3}. Retournez-la à tout moment pour son coût de mue.)_#','Erstschlag£Morph {4}{R} #_(Du kannst diese Karte verdeckt für {3} als eine 2/2 Kreatur wirken. Decke sie zu einem beliebigen Zeitpunkt für ihre Morph-Kosten auf.)_#','Attacco improvviso£Metamorfosi {4}{R} #_(Puoi lanciare questa carta a faccia in giù come una creatura 2/2 pagando {3}. Girala a faccia in su in qualsiasi momento pagando il suo costo di metamorfosi.)_#','先制攻撃£変異{4}{R}（あなたはこのカードを、{3}で２/２クリーチャーとして裏向きに唱えてもよい。これの変異コストで、これをいつでも表向きにしてよい。）','Iniciativa£Metamorfose {4}{R} #_(Você pode conjurar este card com a face voltada para baixo como uma criatura 2/2 por {3}. Volte sua face para cima a qualquer momento pagando seu custo de metamorfose.)_#','Первый удар£Оборотень {4}{R} #_(Вы можете разыграть эту карту рубашкой вверх как существо 2/2 за {3}. Переверните ее рубашкой вниз в любой момент за ее стоимость Оборотня.)_#','Daña primero.£Metamorfosis {4}{R}. #_(Puedes lanzar esta carta boca abajo como una criatura 2/2 pagando {3}. Ponla boca arriba en cualquier momento pagando su coste de metamorfosis.)_#','선제공격£변이 {4}{B} #_(당신은 {3}을 지불해서 이 카드를 뒷면 상태의 2/2 생물로 발동할 수 있다. 언제든지 변이 비용을 지불하고 앞면이 보이도록 뒤집을 수 있다.)_#','#_「犬人就是野狗，不配跟我们一起围坐火旁。」£～召猎人苏拉克_#','#_「犬人就是野狗，不配跟我們一起圍坐火旁。」£～召獵人蘇拉克_#','#_« Les aïnoks sont des chiens sauvages qui n''ont pas leur place avec nous près du feu. »£—Surrak, le Grand veneur_#','#_„Die Ainok sind wilde Köter, an unserem Feuer ist kein Platz für sie."£—Surrak der Jagdrufer_#','#_"Gli ainok sono cani selvaggi, non meritano di unirsi a noi intorno al fuoco."£—Surrak, il Convocatore di Caccia_#','#_「アイノクは野犬だ。我らと共に火を囲むのに相応しい存在ではない。」£――狩猟の統率者、スーラク_#','#_"Os ainok são cães selvagens, não são dignos de unir-se a nós ao redor da fogueira."£— Surrak, o Convocador da Caçada_#','#_«Аиноки — это дикие собаки, которым не место у нашего костра».£— Суррак, Созыватель Охоты_#','#_"Los ainok no son más que perros salvajes. No son dignos de sentarse con nosotros en torno al fuego".£—Surrak, la Voz de la caza_#','#_"아이녹은 들개야. 우리와 함께 모닥불 가에 앉을 자격이 없다."£—사냥 대장 서락_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('394066','Altar of the Brood','UGIN','Artifact','R','{1}','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Whenever another permanent enters the battlefield under your control, each opponent puts the top card of their library into their graveyard.','#_Supplicants offer flesh and silver, flowers and blood. The altar takes what it will, eyes gleaming with unspoken promises._#',NULL,'Erica Yang','216','5','£9/20/2014: If Altar of the Brood enters the battlefield under your control at the same time as other permanents, its ability will trigger for each of those permanents.','A',NULL,'8.99','11.99','19.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'族群祭坛','族群祭壇','Autel de la Couvée','Altar der Brut','Altare della Nidiata','群の祭壇','Altar da Linhagem','Алтарь Выводка','Altar de la progenie','군락의 제단','神器','神器','Artefact','Artefakt','Artefatto','アーティファクト','Artefato','Артефакт','Artefacto','마법물체','每当另一个永久物在你的操控下进战场时，每位对手各将其牌库顶牌置入其坟墓场。','每當另一個永久物在你的操控下進戰場時，每位對手各將其牌庫頂牌置入其墳墓場。','À chaque fois qu''un autre permanent arrive le champ de bataille sous votre contrôle, chaque adversaire met la carte du dessus de sa bibliothèque dans son cimetière.','Immer wenn eine andere bleibende Karte unter deiner Kontrolle ins Spiel kommt, legt jeder Gegner die oberste Karte seiner Bibliothek auf seinen Friedhof.','Ogniqualvolta un altro permanente entra nel campo di battaglia sotto il tuo controllo, ogni avversario mette nel proprio cimitero la prima carta del proprio grimorio.','他のパーマネントが１つあなたのコントロール下で戦場に出るたび、各対戦相手はそれぞれ自分のライブラリーの一番上のカードを自分の墓地に置く。','Toda vez que outra permanente entra no campo de batalha sob o seu controle, cada oponente coloca o card do topo do grimório dele no próprio cemitério.','Каждый раз, когда другой перманент выходит на поле битвы под вашим контролем, каждый оппонент кладет верхнюю карту своей библиотеки на свое кладбище.','Siempre que otro permanente entre al campo de batalla bajo tu control, cada oponente pone la primera carta de su biblioteca en su cementerio.','당신의 조종하에 다른 지속물이 전장에 들어올 때마다, 각 상대는 자신의 서고 맨 위의 카드 한 장을 자신의 무덤에 넣는다.','#_祈求者献上鲜肉与白银、鲜花和血液。祭坛取走它想要的，眼睛闪烁着不成文的诺言。_#','#_祈求者獻上鮮肉與白銀、鮮花和血液。祭壇取走它想要的，眼睛閃爍著不成文的諾言。_#','#_Les quémandeurs déposent de la chair et de l''argent, des fleurs et du sang. L''autel prend ce qui lui convient, les yeux luisants de promesses inexprimées._#','#_Bittsteller bringen Fleisch und Silber, Blumen und Blut. Der Altar nimmt sich, was er will, mit glühenden Augen voller Verheißung._#','#_I supplici offrono carne e argento, fiori e sangue. L''altare accetta ciò che predilige, i suoi occhi splendenti di promesse silenziose._#','#_嘆願者は肉や銀や花や血を奉納する。祭壇は望むものを取り、その目は語られざる約束で輝きを放っている。_#','#_Os suplicantes oferecem carne e prata, flores e sangue. O altar recebe o que quer, seus olhos brilhando com promessas veladas._#','#_Просители приносят плоть и серебро, цветы и кровь. Алтарь принимает то, что ему угодно, и его глаза сияют невысказанными обещаниями._#','#_Los suplicantes ofrecen carne y plata, flores y sangre. El altar toma lo que desea y sus ojos brillan con promesas mudas._#','#_집행자는 살점과 은, 꽃, 피를 바친다. 제단은 말없이 약속하는 눈빛을 발하며 원하는 제물을 취한다._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('394067','Arashin War Beast','UGIN','Creature — Beast','U','{5}{G}{G}','7','6','6',NULL,'Whenever Arashin War Beast deals combat damage to one or more blocking creatures, manifest the top card of your library. #_(Put it onto the battlefield face down as a 2/2 creature. Turn it face up any time for its mana cost if it''s a creature card.)_#',NULL,NULL,'Eric Deschamps','123','5','£11/24/2014: Arashin War Beast’s ability will trigger only once per combat damage step, no matter how many creatures are blocking it.£11/24/2014: The face-down permanent is a 2/2 creature with no name, mana cost, creature types, or abilities. It’s colorless and has a converted mana cost of 0. Other effects that apply to the permanent can still grant or change any of these characteristics.£11/24/2014: Any time you have priority, you may turn a manifested creature face up by revealing that it’s a creature card (ignoring any copy effects or type-changing effects that might be applying to it) and paying its mana cost. This is a special action. It doesn’t use the stack and can’t be responded to.£11/24/2014: If a manifested creature would have morph if it were face up, you may also turn it face up by paying its morph cost.£11/24/2014: Unlike a face-down creature that was cast using the morph ability, a manifested creature may still be turned face up after it loses its abilities if it’s a creature card.£11/24/2014: Because the permanent is on the battlefield both before and after it’s turned face up, turning a permanent face up doesn’t cause any enters-the-battlefield abilities to trigger.£11/24/2014: Because face-down creatures don’t have names, they can’t have the same name as any other creature, even another face-down creature.£11/24/2014: A permanent that turns face up or face down changes characteristics but is otherwise the same permanent. Spells and abilities that were targeting that permanent, as well as Auras and Equipment that were attached to the permanent, aren’t affected.£11/24/2014: Turning a permanent face up or face down doesn’t change whether that permanent is tapped or untapped.£11/24/2014: At any time, you can look at a face-down permanent you control. You can’t look at face-down permanents you don’t control unless an effect allows you to or instructs you to.£11/24/2014: If a face-down permanent you control leaves the battlefield, you must reveal it. You must also reveal all face-down spells and permanents you control if you leave the game or if the game ends.£11/24/2014: You must ensure that your face-down spells and permanents can easily be differentiated from each other. You’re not allowed to mix up the cards that represent them on the battlefield in order to confuse other players. The order they entered the battlefield should remain clear. Common methods for indicating this include using markers or dice, or simply placing them in order on the battlefield. You must also track how each became face down (manifested, cast face down using the morph ability, and so on).£11/24/2014: There are no cards in the Fate Reforged set that would turn a face-down instant or sorcery card on the battlefield face up, but some older cards can try to do this. If something tries to turn a face-down instant or sorcery card on the battlefield face up, reveal that card to show all players it’s an instant or sorcery card. The permanent remains on the battlefield face down. Abilities that trigger when a permanent turns face up won’t trigger, because even though you revealed the card, it never turned face up.£11/24/2014: Some older Magic sets feature double-faced cards, which have a Magic card face on each side rather than a Magic card face on one side and a Magic card back on the other. The rules for double-faced cards are changing slightly to account for the possibility that they are manifested. If a double-faced card is manifested, it will be put onto the battlefield face down. While face down, it can’t transform. If the front face of the card is a creature card, you can turn it face up by paying its mana cost. If you do, its front face will be up. A double-faced permanent on the battlefield still can’t be turned face down.','G',NULL,'0.03','0.62','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'G','阿拉辛战争兽','阿拉辛戰爭獸','Bête de guerre d''Arashin','Arashin-Kriegsbestie','Bestia da Guerra di Arashin','アラシンの軍獣','Fera de Guerra Arashin','Арашинский Боевой Зверь','Bestia de guerra de Arashin','아라신 전쟁 야수','生物～野兽','生物～野獸','Créature : bête','Kreatur — Bestie','Creatura — Bestia','クリーチャー ― ビースト','Criatura — Besta','Существо — Зверь','Criatura — Bestia','생물 — 야수','每当阿拉辛战争兽对一个或数个进行阻挡的生物造成战斗伤害时，显化你的牌库顶牌。（将它面朝下地放进战场，当成2/2生物。如果该牌是生物牌，则可随时支付其法术力费用使其翻回正面。）','每當阿拉辛戰爭獸對一個或數個進行阻擋的生物造成戰鬥傷害時，顯化你的牌庫頂牌。（將它面朝下地放進戰場，當成2/2生物。如果該牌是生物牌，則可隨時支付其魔法力費用使其翻回正面。）','À chaque fois que la Bête de guerre d''Arashin inflige des blessures de combat à au moins une créature bloqueuse, manifestez la carte du dessus de votre bibliothèque. #_(Mettez-la sur le champ de bataille face cachée comme une créature 2/2. Retournez-la face visible à tout moment pour son coût de mana si c''est une carte de créature.)_#','Immer wenn die Arashin-Kriegsbestie einer oder mehreren blockenden Kreaturen Kampfschaden zufügt, manifestiere die oberste Karte deiner Bibliothek. #_(Bringe sie als eine 2/2 Kreatur verdeckt ins Spiel. Decke sie zu einem bel